Class avfilter.AVFilterBufferRefVideoProps

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.javacpp.avfilter.AVFilterBufferRefVideoProps
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    avfilter

    public static class avfilter.AVFilterBufferRefVideoProps
extends Pointer
    Video specific properties in a reference to an AVFilterBuffer. Since AVFilterBufferRef is common to different media formats, video specific per reference properties must be separated out.
